cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision): The paper proposes a deep fashion item encoder that exploits visual features to represent fashion products. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes a novel framework that jointly optimizes fashion item embeddings and category-specific complementary relations via end-to-end learning. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval): The paper addresses the task of identifying mix-and-match relationships between fashion items in a fashion e-commerce recommender system. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language): The paper uses textual features to represent fashion products in the proposed deep fashion item encoder. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper deals with fashion items, which can be considered as a type of multimedia content.
